# Automated AI Digital Content Creator

This project automates the creation, packaging, and sale of digital products based on trending topics, using AI and social media trends.

## Features

- Weekly detection of trending topics (Twitter, Reddit)
- AI-powered e-book/template/content generation
- Automated uploading to Gumroad (or other platforms)
- Automated marketing (social media, email)
- Modular & extensible for new platforms or content types

## Architecture

```mermaid
graph TD;
    A[Trend Detection] --> B[AI Content Generation]
    B --> C[Design Generation (Visuals)]
    C --> D[Product Packaging & Upload]
    D --> E[Automated Marketing]
    E --> F[Sales & Feedback Collection]
    F --> A
```

## Getting Started

1. Clone the repo  
2. Copy `.env.example` to `.env` and fill in your API keys  
3. Install dependencies:  
   ```bash
   pip install -r requirements.txt
   ```
4. Run the workflow:  
   ```bash
   python src/main.py
   ```

## Customization

- Add more trend sources (TikTok, Google Trends, etc.)
- Add more sales platforms (Etsy, Shopify, etc.)
- Expand AI content types (templates, courses, etc.)

